          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-09-03T20:47:24Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Veterans Valuing Our Widows and Widowers Act or the Veterans VOW Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the payment of a Medal of Honor special pension to the surviving spouse of a deceased Medal of Honor recipient if that person was married to the recipient for (1) at least one year prior to the veteran's death; or (2) any period of time if a child was born of the marriage or was born to them before the marriage.</p> <p>The bill increases the special pension for a living Medal of Honor recipient to $1329.58 per month. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-08-24T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
